result.name: Genome-wide identification of SNPs in pikeperch
result.description: Identification of single nucleotide polymorphisms (SNPs) in whole-genome sequencing data of pikeperch (Sander lucioperca). The publication related to the project is "An ultra-high density SNP-based linkage map for enhancing the pikeperch (Sander lucioperca) genome assembly to chromosome-scale".
result.center: Leibniz Institute for Farm Animal Biology (FBN)
